Michigan to see them.

42:31.366 --> 42:36.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: A fiery red sky,
people trapped in a burning
city, charred remains from the

42:38.366 --> 42:42.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
