43:46.266 --> 43:48.133 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
A rebellion?

43:48.133 --> 43:50.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Even a revolution?

43:50.166 --> 43:54.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And using art to
look back and ahead.

43:54.500 --> 43:59.266 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
At the Detroit Historical
Museum, which, for
the record, has been a
funder of the "NewsHour"

43:59.266 --> 44:04.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
and which spearheaded
