TVs play news footage.

44:04.166 --> 44:09.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A replica of a National Guard
tank has been turned into an
audiovisual experience, with

44:10.266 --> 44:14.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
