told by Detroiters.

44:14.466 --> 44:19.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Detroit Institute of Art
weighs in with an exhibition
titled Art of Rebellion: Black

44:21.333 --> 44:25.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Art of the Civil Rights Movement
with works by individuals,
